metadata.name: Sea-Monster Carrying a Woman on a Shell
metadata.description:
Sea-Monster Carrying a Woman on a Shell Flanked by a Triton and a Man with an Oar. 
Digital sculpture based on a scene from a famous engraving created in 1582 by Adrian Kollaert and Hans Kollaert the Elder. 
Created in 2022. All parts were made by me from scratch.
